snippet.title: Worms WMD: Mobilize - Android Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is the mobile port of Worms W.M.D., but due to the mobile nature, there is no crafting and you can only have four worms in a team rather than eight.

Worms, Worms W.M.D., Worms WMD: Mobilize © Team17
Also released on iOS
